parameters:
\SE[7]I'm sorry... I should have told you that staying in
hot water for a long time can give you \!\SM[nod]\SE[38]a
case of hot water sickness....

\SE[7]No... I'm fine. \SM[nod]\SE[1]Taking a bath felt
good...

\SE[6]It would be nice to feel the wind a little. \SE[0]From
here, you can see the Mottrell Mine and the night view is
beautiful, I think.

Oh, you're right.... Can you see something in the
distance...?

\SE[0]I'll turn off the lights. \.If I do that, it will look
even more beautiful.
\SE[2]... How about now? \!\SE[1] Can you see something?

\SM[jump]\SE[2]Ah, I can see it clearly now...
Amazing.... \SE[2]It's beautiful... I wonder what that light
is....

\SE[2]Streetlights that illuminate the road. \SE[1]They were
created by the country for nighttime safety.

\SE[5]Wow... it's really beautiful.... \!\SE[2]I wonder what
that is... the light is flickering....

\SE[0]This is the entrance to the mine. \SE[0]It's made
easy to understand so that people who are not familiar with
the area don't enter.

\SE[21]I feel a little relieved. \!\SE[20]And then, just a
little...

\SM[nod]\SE[50]Somehow, I feel like I'm about to cry.
\!\SE[37]Just for a little while... Can I stay like this...?

\SE[29]You've always protected me until now.
\!\SM[nod]\SE[83]Thank you... Luna...

\SE[37]......\.......\........ \!\SE[50]Did you think I was
going to make you cry just now?

\SE[2]This might be the first time I've come this far
away. I haven't really left the village much... \SE[2]What
about you, Luna? Have you been here before?

\SE[6]I learned about it in school, so I know the names of
the places, but I haven't actually been there much...
\SE[2]I've been studying all the time...

\SM[jump]\SE[21]I see... That's good.
\SM[jump]\SE[21]Then, the two of us can create lots of
firsts together.

\SM[jump]Huh...! \SE[13]No way...! \SM[double]\SE[116]I
didn't mean it like that at all! \SM[double]\SE[116]Ehh!
\SM[double]\SE[116]Nooo wayyy...!

\SM[jump]Mou! Luna has become mean! \!\SE[17]She became a
bad girl at school!!
L-Luna... um... still... \SE[93] about that time...
Um, um...? \SE[93] About when we were kids... umm...

\SM[jump]Hauu...!! \.W-wait...! \.Don't guess...!
\!\SM[rock]\SE[95]My face is turning bright red...!!

\SE[46]Laura... you remembered too. \SE[37]I was a little
worried about what would happen if you had forgotten.

\SM[double]\SE[16]W-well, there's no way I would forget...!
\SE[92]Because I... I said let's get married...
\SM[nod]\SE[15]Oh, that's right... Hehe... I was happy.

\SM[nod]\SE[45]Yes... even now... \SE[46]forever...
forever... I've always loved you...
\SM[double]Ahh...!! No... I can't show you my face...!

\SE[47]That much...? \SE[45]I want to keep looking at
Laura's face forever...

\SM[rock]Uuu... Luna is unfair... \SE[92]She's become so
amazing at the school... She's cool and always helps me...
\SE[45]Is that so...? \.I find Laura attractive, though...

\SE[90]No... I'm happy... really happy... \!\SE[91]But...
I'm a little... too happy... and it's making me dizzy...

\SE[46]Hehe... I'm sorry? \SE[15]I was also... so happy to
finally meet you...

Ahh... Somehow, I... \SE[85]feel light-headed... I'm getting
all fuzzy-headed...

\SE[46]Did I tire you out a bit...? \!\SE[45]Should we take
a rest on the bed for a while...?

Laura has climbed a little on the Adult Stairs! She has
learned the Sword Technique \i[404] Cheerful Élair!
